text: Albertine Anne Thackwell was an archer from Great Britain. She was born on 19 June 1863 and died on 22 September 1944. Thackwell competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Albertine ThackwellAlbertine THACKWELL == References == Category:1863 births Category:1944 deaths Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
